This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as relation extraction and question answering, which are typically covered under the arXiv sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models and techniques, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval and text classification, which are relevant to the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
